title: Reclaiming of Duback
description: "There are so many experiences one faces by oneself. These experiences are the hidden events that complete life in-between living within the physical. The little things that are not meant to be shared with physical entities. The secret happenings within your deepest Self. These are my experiences I did not originally want to share with this World. I am Han, and this is my life-memory . . . " - Han StormThe Chronicles of Han, Reclaiming of Duback, is the conclusion to Book 1 and a continuation of the adventures of Han Storm, an extraordinary psychic. Join Han in this relentless, non-stop, fast-paced adventure in securing a new Planetary Home Base for his people. This volume includes the 'Who-is-Who' in Han's World!Available direct from author www.chroniclesofhan.com
author: H.  Gibson
